","chapter":114,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So Moses took the staff from the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s presence "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 17:10","book":"Num","chapter":17,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" just as he had commanded him. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 17:10","book":"Num","chapter":17,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Moses and Aaron summoned the assembly in front of the rock, and Moses said to them, “Listen, you rebels! Must we bring water out of this rock for you?” "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then Moses raised his hand and struck the rock twice with his staff, so that abundant water gushed out, and the community and their livestock drank. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 17:6","book":"Exo","chapter":17,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 78:15","book":"Psa","chapter":78,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 10:4","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":4,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 17:6","book":"Exo","chapter":17,"verse":6},{"label":"Ps 78:15","book":"Psa","chapter":78,"verse":15},{"label":"1Co 10:4","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" said to Moses and Aaron, “Because you did not trust me to demonstrate my holiness in the sight of the Israelites, you will not bring this assembly into the land I have given them.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 27:12","book":"Num","chapter":27,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 1:37","book":"Deu","chapter":1,"verse":37,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 3:26","book":"Deu","chapter":3,"verse":26,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:51","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":51,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 27:12","book":"Num","chapter":27,"verse":12},{"label":"Dt 1:37","book":"Deu","chapter":1,"verse":37},{"label":"Dt 3:26","book":"Deu","chapter":3,"verse":26},{"label":"Dt 32:51","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":51}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"These are the Waters of Meribah, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"= Quarreling"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 17:7","book":"Exo","chapter":17,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 27:14","book":"Num","chapter":27,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:51","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":51,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 95:8","book":"Psa","chapter":95,"verse":8,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 106:32","book":"Psa","chapter":106,"verse":32,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" where the Israelites quarreled with the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", and he demonstrated his holiness to them. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 27:14","book":"Num","chapter":27,"verse":14,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 28:22","book":"Ezk","chapter":28,"verse":22,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 38:23","book":"Ezk","chapter":38,"verse":23,"letter":"h"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 17:7","book":"Exo","chapter":17,"verse":7},{"label":"Nm 27:14","book":"Num","chapter":27,"verse":14},{"label":"Dt 32:51","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":51},{"label":"Ps 95:8","book":"Psa","chapter":95,"verse":8},{"label":"Ps 106:32","book":"Psa","chapter":106,"verse":32},{"label":"Nm 27:14","book":"Num","chapter":27,"verse":14},{"label":"Ezk 28:22","book":"Ezk","chapter":28,"verse":22},{"label":"Ezk 38:23","book":"Ezk","chapter":38,"verse":23}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"= Quarreling"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Moses sent messengers from Kadesh to the king of Edom, “This is what your brother Israel "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 25:23–26","book":"Gen","chapter":25,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 25:30","book":"Gen","chapter":25,"verse":30,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 36:8","book":"Gen","chapter":36,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" says, ‘You know all the hardships that have overtaken us. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 25:23–26","book":"Gen","chapter":25,"verse":23},{"label":"Gn 25:30","book":"Gen","chapter":25,"verse":30},{"label":"Gn 36:8","book":"Gen","chapter":36,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Our ancestors went down to Egypt, and we lived in Egypt many years, but the Egyptians treated us and our ancestors badly. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When we cried out to the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", he heard our plea, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit voice"},{"kind":"text","text":" and sent an angel, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or a messenger"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 3:7–10","book":"Exo","chapter":3,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 14:19","book":"Exo","chapter":14,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 23:20","book":"Exo","chapter":23,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and brought us out of Egypt. Now look, we are in Kadesh, a city on the border of your territory. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 3:7–10","book":"Exo","chapter":3,"verse":7},{"label":"Ex 14:19","book":"Exo","chapter":14,"verse":19},{"label":"Ex 23:20","book":"Exo","chapter":23,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit voice"},{"marker":2,"text":"Or a messenger"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Please let us travel through your land. We won’t travel through any field or vineyard, or drink any well water. We will travel the King’s Highway; we won’t turn to the right or the left until we have traveled through your territory.’” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 21:22","book":"Num","chapter":21,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 2:27","book":"Deu","chapter":2,"verse":27,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 21:22","book":"Num","chapter":21,"verse":22},{"label":"Dt 2:27","book":"Deu","chapter":2,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But Edom answered him, “You will not travel through our land, or we will come out and confront you with the sword.”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“We will go on the main road,” the Israelites replied to them, “and if we or our herds drink your water, we will pay its price. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 2:1","book":"Deu","chapter":2,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" There will be no problem; only let us travel through on foot.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 2:1","book":"Deu","chapter":2,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Yet Edom insisted, “You may not travel through.” And they came out to confront them with a large force of heavily-armed people. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit with numerous people and a strong hand"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit with numerous people and a strong hand"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Edom refused to allow Israel to travel through their territory, and Israel turned away from them."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"After they set out from Kadesh, the entire Israelite community came to Mount Hor. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 21:4","book":"Num","chapter":21,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 33:37–41","book":"Num","chapter":33,"verse":37,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:50","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":50,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 21:4","book":"Num","chapter":21,"verse":4},{"label":"Nm 33:37–41","book":"Num","chapter":33,"verse":37},{"label":"Dt 32:50","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":50}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" said to Moses and Aaron at Mount Hor on the border of the land of Edom, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Aaron will be gathered to his people; he will not enter the land I have given the Israelites, because you both rebelled against my command at the Waters of Meribah. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Take Aaron and his son Eleazar and bring them up Mount Hor. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Remove Aaron’s garments and put them on his son Eleazar. Aaron will be gathered to his people and die there.”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So Moses did as the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" commanded, and they climbed Mount Hor in the sight of the whole community. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"After Moses removed Aaron’s garments and put them on his son Eleazar, Aaron died there on top of the mountain. Then Moses and Eleazar came down from the mountain. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Num:20:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When the whole community saw that Aaron had passed away, the entire house of Israel mourned for him thirty days."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279347559}